{"type":"text","timestamp":1775863338565,"sessionID":"ses_286514219ffeo0SiZh53PR0xDV","part":{"id":"prt_d79b400bf001Shinb48TNITyec","messageID":"msg_d79b3f854001HKeuZrTT2yZKQa","sessionID":"ses_286514219ffeo0SiZh53PR0xDV","type":"text","text":"Implementation complete. Here's a summary of what was created:\n\n## AR-018 — Agentd Idle Cleanup Controller\n\n### Files Created\n\n**`pkg/agentd/constants.go`**\n- `SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute`\n- `LastActivityAnnotationKey = \"last-activity-time\"`\n- `DefaultRequeueInterval = 30 * time.Second`\n\n**`pkg/agentd/controller.go`**\n- `Sandbox` and `SandboxList` types for `agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1`\n- `Reconciler` with `Reconcile()` method implementing idle detection logic\n- `SetupWithManager()` for controller registration\n- Reads `last-activity-time` annotation, parses RFC3339 timestamp\n- Deletes Sandbox when idle > 15 minutes\n- Requeues until expiration when not yet idle\n- Handles NotFound errors gracefully\n\n**`pkg/agentd/controller_test.go`** (16 test cases)\n- NotFound, missing annotation, empty annotation\n- Invalid timestamp parsing\n- Not expired, expired, near expiration\n- Multiple namespaces, timezones\n- DeepCopy validation\n\n**`cmd/agentd/main.go`**\n- Controller-runtime manager setup\n- Scheme registration with Sandbox types\n- Reconciler registration\n- Signal handling for graceful shutdown\n\n### Test Results\n```\nPASS - 16/16 tests passed\nBuild - SUCCESS\n```","time":{"start":1775863338564,"end":1775863338564}}}
